(4460, '230pj', '2016-01-11 00:05:24', 't_mid.1452387274874:ef96421d02d0046f64', 'i', '3', '', 'Ang available ko lang po na makukuhang subjects ay worth 9 units lang po (3 subjects) over 13 maximum units this semester. Naging result po yan ng  nagdrop po ako ng isang seasonal subject nung 2nd year student po ako and nagfollow na po ang pagiging delayed student ko po sa BS MST curriculum.', '19', 'm_mid.1452441918160:f291e7895e5eecb029', '{"name":"Carl Kenneth Reyes","email":null,"fbuserid":"100000259609368"}'),
