(5055, '0j8ld', '2016-01-18 09:07:59', 't_mid.1452960001786:f6cbe06539ddaa0893', 'o', '4', 'rpsolis@uplbosa.org', 'You can download the University Clearance from www.uplbosa.org.\r\nFirst, login the site using your SystemOne username and password (since you have SystemOne account). Second, update your profile. Then, you can find the University Clearance by clicking Student Menu > University Clearance. Generate it and print. Thanks!', '', '', ''),
