(5059, 'nq8t3', '2016-01-18 09:27:40', '09777882503', 'o', '4', 'rpsolis@uplbosa.org', 'If you recently encountered a difficult situation that affected your capability to pay your matriculation fees, you may draft a letter addressed to the "ST Chairperson" and submit it to Room 5, 2/F SU Building not later than 22 January 2016. This will be reviewed by the Committee on Scholarships and Financial Assistance. You will receive a text message regarding the committee\'s action on your request. Thank you.', '', '', ''),
