(5158, 'netxc', '2016-01-19 15:41:25', 't_mid.1453181428231:51556dd092d226f772', 'o', '4', 'rpsolis@uplbosa.org', 'The deadline for STS application and appeal was last Semester. But, if  you recently encountered a difficult situation that affected your capability to pay your matriculation fees, you may draft a letter addressed to the "ST Chairperson" and submit it to Room 5, 2/F SU Building not later than 22 January 2016. This will be reviewed by the Committee on Scholarships and Financial Assistance.', '', '', ''),
