(5216, 'nkdwr', '2016-01-21 11:28:49', 't_mid.1453344065807:d69d5e1e14ee108d81', 'i', '3', '', 'Hi. Good Morning. I\'m Lanie from ICS. I would just like to report a bug in the SA Portal page for SA Supervisors. After answering the quiz, When I click the submit button, nothing happens. No notifications or whatsoever whether I got all the items correct or not. Hope you can assist me with this one. Thanks. :)', '1', 'm_mid.1453344065807:d69d5e1e14ee108d81', '{"name":"Lanie Danila","email":null,"fbuserid":"10205657672508790"}'),
