(5218, 'nkdwr', '2016-01-21 11:53:59', 't_mid.1453344065807:d69d5e1e14ee108d81', 'o', '4', 'mvasantos@uplbosa.org', 'Good morning Prof. Danila!\r\n\r\nWe tried answering the quiz displayed by our system. However, we cannot replicate the issue you are experiencing - we are always getting the expected response from the system. There was also no recent change in our system that could have affected the SA quiz. Our system logs also show that there are at least three other employees who were able to complete the quiz in the past hour.\r\n\r\nAfter clicking the submit button, you should be prompted by a confirmation dialog box saying "Are you sure?" After confirming, you should be prompted with either a red box or a green box on top saying something like:\r\n[red box]: Your answer in question #X is wrong. Please review your answer.\r\n[green box]: Congratulations! You passed the quiz. The SA item codes are displayed below.\r\n\r\nIt is possible that the page did not completely load or that the problem is caused by the intermittent Internet connection of the University.\r\n\r\nWould it be okay if you try to reload the page and try to answer the form again?\r\n\r\nIf you still experience the same problem, we advise you to use the \'Report Problem\' feature at the lower right of the website. This feature allows us to see a screen shot of the site from your perspective.\r\n\r\nThank you!', '', '', ''),
