(5433, 'cahtm', '2016-01-25 14:23:41', 't_mid.1453703015670:f4c3e80d58b2194e38', 'i', '3', '', 'Good day, UPLB OSA. I am Joseph Roble, a URA from the Office of Public Relations.\n\nI have recently claimed the alloted hours for my SA and have already entered the code. However, I will be transferring to DevCom soon. \n\nIn this light, I would like to ask if there\'s a process that would allow me to transfer my allotted hours to one of my officemates?\n\nThank you very much.', '19', 'm_mid.1453703015670:f4c3e80d58b2194e38', '{"name":"Chad Roble","email":null,"fbuserid":"10201340007018660"}'),
(5434, 'cahtm', '2016-01-25 14:46:50', 't_mid.1453703015670:f4c3e80d58b2194e38', 'o', '4', 'mvasantos@uplbosa.org', 'Hi Joseph! You can use the \'Share AH\' feature in the SA Portal. Just log in to www.uplbosa.org/hire, click Share AH, then provide the email address of your office mate. Also, as soon as you assume your new position at CDC, please let us know so we can update your records as an SA supervisor. Thanks and have a great day!', '', '', ''),
