(6388, 'd2jhc', '2016-02-27 14:05:26', 't_mid.1456553123333:698f8d3cf9d3e72d48', 'i', '3', '', 'Dear family and friends:\n \nI am Patrick Jimenez  from the TRILLANES FOR VICE PRESIDENT CAMPAIGN. As part of our initiative to engage the electorate and support Antonio "Sonny" F. Trillanes IV in his bid for Vice Presidency, we are sending you a summary of his educational and professional background, as well as his legislative accomplishments.\n \nFor the past eight years, Senator Trillanes has stood with us in the fight against systemic corruption. As an advocate of good governance, he has championed the cause of the civil servants, fought for accessible and affordable basic social services, and represented the common peoples aspirations. Today, let us stand for Senator Trillanes.\n \nAs such, we call on all citizens to join us and rally behind Senator Trillanes in his march to the vice presidency.\n \nYour support can make a huge difference. We invite you, along with your family and friends, to join us as we strive to make the country a better place.\n \nThank you and God bless!', '19', 'm_mid.1456553123333:698f8d3cf9d3e72d48', '{"name":"Patrick Jimenez","email":null,"fbuserid":"151312141923080"}'),
